I write on twitter (@sainteclectic) to help teach people about blockchain & NFTs because I am passionate about crypto & sharing. I am in debt because I borrowed to farm USDC believing it was audited and safe which is why I concentrated more into the pool over time. This was not wise & a big mistake and I’ve learned a very painful lesson. My wife & I are starting a family so I farmed stables to try and help build our funds up steadily.

We're late to crypto(Dec2020)&everything invested is from employment & years of hard work, not large crypto gains. She works hours in healthcare & I help manage her funds. I regret compromising our future. I am not coping very well and have taken time off work to help the situation & community. Thank you for hearing us & considering a compassionate approach.
